			<sentence id="2.1">In an attempt to learn more about Apache, i reinstalled it on my home network, 
yet was forced to remove it once again.</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.2">Like last time i lost my settings and 
so internet sharing was lost within the network.</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.3">It took me 3 hours of playing 
with dns, ips, and gateways to get the computers to see each other again.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
